73083926ff6c1b0d2d508822eb18","tid":1663171,"uid":41477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"旺角個d售票增值機壞左成個月都無處理，剩係入閘收錢就識加塊硬膠保護"},{"pid":"3e0e0df21458275ea65055be5876b319fd86f538","tid":1663171,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4473811835658c86dd1cf8c5a23b95b4cc64edb8","tid":1663171,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:56:21.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"069a392c2828c6a253ff5b73f977058579e1afc3","tid":1663171,"uid":52283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:56:25.000Z","msg":"開比你返工，收工準時返屋企，明未？<br />\n如果開唔到你直情返唔到工啦"},{"pid":"f789949f5df5092bd37c39417f9140cbd8247cd5","tid":1663171,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:05:05.000Z","msg":"修復係藉口，完全唔見有野修復過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a882e9e7e7b4d372fdc8c5425019aaebac3e8ca","tid":1663171,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfc419033085ce23075fd83bae6b6099ccec554","tid":1663171,"uid":325098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:23:52.000Z